      "content": "i get that, but my doctor is literally impossible to reach after 5pm and i'm already feeling a bit lightheaded. if i take the full dose after only eating a salad, i'm way more scared of crashing in my sleep than i am of my sugar being high. wouldn't it make more sense to just skip it for tonight and get back to normal tomorrow?",
